thread.title: BRIEF-Changzhou Qianhong Biopharma sees FY 2018 H1 net profit up 10 pct to 30 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Changzhou Qianhong Biopharma sees FY 2018 H1 net profit up 10 pct to 30 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - changzhou qianhong biopharma co ltd

text:
April 20(Reuters) - Changzhou Qianhong Biopharma Co Ltd
* Sees FY 2018 H1 net profit to increase by 10 percent to 30 percent, or to be 158.4 million yuan to 187.2 million yuan
* Says FY 2017 H1 net profit was 144 million yuan
